24. What is diff between kubectl apply and kubectl create/update
  Use kubectl create when you are certain the resource doesnâ€™t exist and you are creating it for the first time.
  Use kubectl apply for both creation and updates. Itâ€™s the recommended command for declarative configuration management
  and handling changes over time.

